(1183, 'NXT', 'Nxt', '1183-NXT.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoS/LPoS', 'http://nxt.org/', 'nxtcommunity', '<p>Nxt is considered a 2nd generation crypto currency. With all the alt coins that alter parametes such as hashing mechanism, time between blocks, starting difficulty, and so on, Nxt brings much much more to the table and was designed this way for a number of reasons. It&#39;s proof of stake model makes it less susceptible to 51% attacks whilst it is designed to support large transaction volumes, something which the traditional Bitcoin and its clones have as a potential flaw. Nxt allows the creation and exchange of custom tokens, coloured coins and assets on the Blockchain.</p><p>In 2016, the NXT team announced the launch of Ardor, the Nxt 2.0. The platform will allow users the same features as Nxt and additional tools like sidechain support for asset issuance and more. The destribution of the ARDR token was done through a snapshot process, which is the reason for the price spike during late 2016.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1000000000.00, NULL, 'CCEX~NXT~ETH,Cryptsy~NXT~USD,CCEDK~NXT~USD,CCEDK~NXT~DKK,BTER~NXT~CNY,CCEDK~NXT~CNY,CCEX~NXT~DOGE,Poloniex~NXT~XUSD,Cryptsy~NXT~BTC,CCEDK~NXT~GBP,LiveCoin~NXT~BTC,Poloniex~NXT~USD,Poloniex~NXT~XMR,CCEX~NXT~LTC,CCEX~NXT~BTC,CCEDK~NXT~BTC,Poloniex~NXT~BTC,CCEDK~NXT~RUB,HitBTC~NXT~USD,Cryptsy~NXT~XRP,HitBTC~NXT~ETH,BitTrex~NXT~USD,BitTrex~NXT~BTC,BTER~NXT~BTC,BTC38~NXT~CNY,CCEDK~NXT~LTC,BitSquare~NXT~BTC,Jubi~NXT~CNY,HitBTC~NXT~BTC,CCEX~NXT~USD,Cryptsy~NXT~LTC,BTC38~NXT~BTC,CCEDK~NXT~EUR', 0),
(2349, 'PPC', 'PeerCoin', '2349-PPC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'http://peercoin.net/', 'peercoinppc', '<p>A peer-to-peer crypto-currency design derived from Satoshi Nakamoto&#39;s Bitcoin. Proof-of-Stake replaces Proof-of-Work to provide most of the network security. Under this hybrid design proof-of-work mainly provides initial minting and is largely non-essential in the long run. Security level of the network is not highly enery dependent thus providing an energy efficient and more cost-competitive peer-to-peer crypto-currency. Proof-of-Stake is based on coin age and generated by each node via a hashing scheme bearing similarity to Bitcoins but over limited search space. Block chain history and transaction settlement are further protected by a centrally broadcasted checkpoint mechanism.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bleutrade~PPC~BTC,TradeSatoshi~PPC~USDT,Cryptopia~PPC~UNO,HitBTC~PPC~BTC,LiveCoin~PPC~USD,Cryptopia~PPC~XMR,Coinse~PPC~BTC,HitBTC~PPC~USD,Coinse~PPC~XPM,Cryptsy~PPC~BTC,Novaexchange~PPC~LTC,Cryptopia~PPC~DOGE,Novaexchange~PPC~BTC,Cryptopia~PPC~DOT,Bleutrade~PPC~ETH,Yobit~PPC~DOGE,TheRockTrading~PPC~EUR,Yobit~PPC~ETH,Cryptsy~PPC~XRP,Yobit~PPC~BTC,BTER~PPC~CNY,Cryptopia~PPC~BTC,Cryptopia~PPC~LTC,CCEDK~PPC~BTC,Cryptsy~PPC~USD,TuxExchange~PPC~BTC,TheRockTrading~PPC~BTC,BTER~PPC~BTC,TradeSatoshi~PPC~DOGE,Cryptopia~PPC~ETH,BitTrex~PPC~BTC,BTCE~PPC~USD,Cryptsy~PPC~LTC,LiveCoin~PPC~BTC,Yobit~PPC~RUR,Cryptopia~PPC~FTC,BitZ~PPC~BTC,CCEDK~PPC~CNY,CCEDK~PPC~LTC,Cryptopia~PPC~POP,Yobit~PPC~USD,Bleutrade~PPC~DOGE,TradeSatoshi~PPC~BCH,TradeSatoshi~PPC~BTC,BTC38~PPC~CNY,CCEDK~PPC~EUR,Novaexchange~PPC~ETH,Jubi~PPC~CNY,Yobit~PPC~WAVES,Poloniex~PPC~BTC,BTCE~PPC~BTC,BXinth~PPC~BTC,CCEDK~PPC~RUB,TradeSatoshi~PPC~LTC,CCEDK~PPC~DKK,CCEDK~PPC~USD', 0),
(3638, 'PRC', 'ProsperCoin', '3638-PRC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', NULL, 'prospercoin', '<p>ProsperCoin is a PoW cryptocurrency with a modified Scrypt algorithm. Created to bring to bring prosperity to its users, PRC can be sent to anyone for a small fee and almost instantly.</p>', NULL, NULL, 21000000.00, NULL, 'Poloniex~PRC~BTC,CCEX~PRC~USD,CCEX~PRC~DOGE,CCEX~PRC~BTC,CCEX~PRC~LTC', 0),
(3639, 'YBC', 'YbCoin', '3639-YBC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'http://www.ybcoin.com/en/', 'ybcoin', '<p>YB coin is a Chinese clone of YACcoin. It uses scrypt N+1 and ChaCha. The coin has a relatively low block time at 60 seconds but being a clone hasnt really brought much to the table in terms of innovation. Again like Yacoin there is a dynamically adjusted economic model related to the network power that balances the incentivisation to mine and use it depending on its popularity. An inverse relationship.</p>', NULL, NULL, 200000000.00, NULL, 'BTC38~YBC~CNY,Yobit~YBC~WAVES,BitTrex~YBC~BTC,Cryptsy~YBC~BTC,Yobit~YBC~ETH,Yobit~YBC~DOGE,Yobit~YBC~USD,Yobit~YBC~BTC,Yobit~YBC~RUR', 0),
(3640, 'DANK', 'DarkKush', '3640-DANK.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', NULL, 'DarkKushDANK', '<p><span></span>DarkKush is a cryptocurrency built for the marijuana community, it&#39;s a PoW/PoS hybrid coin.</p>', NULL, '<p><strong>Block Reward:</strong><br /><span>Block 1 - 499 (2000 DarkKush)</span><br /><span>Block 500 - 1999 (1000 DarkKush)</span><br /><span>Block 2000 - 3999 (500 DarkKush)</span><br /><span>Block 4000 - 5999 (250 DarkKush)</span><br /><span>Block 6000 - 7999 (150 DarkKush)</span><br /><span>Block 8000 - 9999 (100 DarkKush)</span><br /><span>Block 10000 - 12499 (50 DarkKush)   </span><br /><span>Block 12000 - 15000 (25 DarkKush)</span></p>', 3000000.00, NULL, 'BitTrex~DANK~BTC', 0),
(3641, 'GIVE', 'GiveCoin', '3641-GIVE.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', NULL, NULL, '<p>GiveCoin is a CryptoCurrency with a charitable angle - the idea being to emPoWer charities and encourage giving. The coin is based on DarkCoins ASIC resistant X11 algorithm, has a block time of 60 seconds - block reward of 1000 coins per block - halving every six months - a total supply of 500 million and a Kimoto gravity well difficulty retargetting. There was a premine of 5%, 2% will be donated to charities on a most voted basis each month, 1% for disaster relief, 1% for bugs and bounties and 1% for development and marketing.</p>', NULL, NULL, 500000000.00, NULL, 'BitTrex~GIVE~BTC', 0),
(3642, 'KOBO', 'KoboCoin', '3642-KOBO.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://kobocoin.com', 'kobocoindev', '<p>Kobocoin is a digital currency and payment system similar to Bitcoin, with an African heritage. All nodes verify transactions in a public distributed ledger calledthe blockchain. The ledger uses its own unit of account, also called KoboCoin(s). KOBO can be sent to anyone in the world for small fees and almost instantly and can also be used for Micropayments.</p>', NULL, NULL, 350000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~KOBO~UNO,Cryptopia~KOBO~LTC,Cryptopia~KOBO~DOT,Novaexchange~KOBO~DOGE,Novaexchange~KOBO~ETH,Cryptopia~KOBO~BTC,Yobit~KOBO~RUR,Yobit~KOBO~DOGE,Cryptopia~KOBO~DOGE,Cryptopia~KOBO~FTC,Yobit~KOBO~WAVES,Novaexchange~KOBO~ESP2,Yobit~KOBO~BTC,Novaexchange~KOBO~BTC,BitTrex~KOBO~BTC,CCEX~KOBO~BTC,Cryptopia~KOBO~XMR,Yobit~KOBO~USD,Yobit~KOBO~ETH', 0),
(3643, 'DT', 'DarkToken', '3643-DT.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', NULL, 'DarkTokenDT', '<p>DarkToken aims to offer a refreshing new take on what a crypto-currency should be by detailing every aspect of the coin, from start to finish. DarkToken takes the next step in coin development by fixing it from the start. Rigorous, energy intensive mining over long periods of time, or even worse, short PoW flash-mines, are extremely detrimental to not only the environment, but the crypto community as a whole. Networks can be maintained perfectly using Proof of Stake.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Cryptsy~DT~BTC,Cryptsy~DT~XRP', 0),
