(4335, 'BCX', 'BattleCoin', '4335-BCX.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoS', 'http://battlecoinxchange.com/', 'BattlecoinBCX', '<p>BXC is also a new fantasy digital currency Battlecoin is a SHA-256 hybrid Proof-of-Work and Proof-of-Stake coin. There is a generous 1% interest for every 10 day period for BCX holders. Battlecoin is a playful coin with serious potential. It has 3% premined coins and 2% of coins given to early adopters. Up untill the 10000th block thereare 500 coins per block, after - only 50 coins per block. It has Proof of Stack feature: Every 10 days 1% of stake is given to the holder if the stake was immovable within 20 days. Block time is 2 minutes and difficulty retargets every 10 blocks.</p>', NULL, NULL, 100000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~BCX~BTC,Gateio~BCX~BTC,Gateio~BCX~USDT', 0),
(4336, 'BEN', 'Benjamins', '4336-BEN.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', NULL, NULL, '<p>Benjamins (BEN) is a SHA based virtual currency based on speed and security. BEN is an alternate currency with 12.8 Million coins available. </p>', NULL, NULL, 12800000.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~BEN~BTC,EtherDelta~BEN~ETH', 0),
(4337, 'BET', 'BetaCoin', '4337-BET.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', NULL, 'Betacoin', '<p>Betacoin is a decentralized Internet currency that enables instant payments to anyone in the world. It is based on the Bitcoin protocol but differs from Bitcoin in some specifications. Betacoin provides faster transaction confirmations (4 minutes average block generating time). The Betacoin network is scheduled to produce 32 million currency units.</p>', NULL, NULL, 32000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~BET~BTC,WavesDEX~BET~BTC,Coinse~BET~BTC,Novaexchange~BET~ESP2,Coinse~BET~LTC,EtherDelta~BET~ETH,HitBTC~BET~ETH', 0),
(4338, 'BITB', 'BitBean', '4338-BITB.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://www.bitbean.org/', 'BitBeanCoin', '<p>BitBean is another alternative crypto currency. Its Proof of Stake is different from other coins. In addition to only giving all coins that have over 6 hours age only 6 hours of age in the PoS calculations, the blocks which are found are static blocks similar to PoW. Each PoS block is 1000 coins.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1000000000.00, NULL, 'Bleutrade~BITB~ETH,Yobit~BITB~BTC,Yobit~BITB~ETH,Novaexchange~BITB~LTC,Yobit~BITB~WAVES,Cryptopia~BITB~DOT,Cryptopia~BITB~LTC,Novaexchange~BITB~PIGGY,Novaexchange~BITB~BTC,Cryptopia~BITB~UNO,Bleutrade~BITB~DOGE,Cryptopia~BITB~FTC,BitTrex~BITB~BTC,Cryptopia~BITB~DOGE,Cryptopia~BITB~BTC,Cryptsy~BITB~BTC,Yobit~BITB~DOGE,Cryptopia~BITB~POP,Cryptopia~BITB~ETH,Novaexchange~BITB~ETH,Novaexchange~BITB~DOGE,Yobit~BITB~USD,Yobit~BITB~RUR,Bleutrade~BITB~BTC,Cryptopia~BITB~XMR', 0),
(4339, 'BLK', 'BlackCoin', '4339-BLK.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoS', 'http://blackcoin.co/', 'CoinBlack', '<p>BlackCoin has seen initial success due to its innovative features. The coin has incorporated bitcoin upgrades to reduce transaction risk. The coin initially uses proof of work as well as proof of stake, with the proof of work being dropped after the 10000th block. The advantages of Blackcoins proof of stake is that it has extremely fast transaction confirmation times at ten seconds - compared to bitcoins ten minutes plus. The other bonus is the low energy consumption without PoW mining. Interest is paid annually at a 1% rate - well below the present global average.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'CCEDK~BLK~DKK,Novaexchange~BLK~BTC,BTC38~BLK~CNY,BTER~BLK~CNY,Cryptopia~BLK~DOGE,Cryptopia~BLK~DOT,Cryptsy~BLK~XRP,Cryptopia~BLK~XMR,TradeSatoshi~BLK~USDT,Novaexchange~BLK~ETH,Novaexchange~BLK~DOGE,Novaexchange~BLK~LTC,Cryptopia~BLK~BTC,BTER~BLK~BTC,Cryptsy~BLK~LTC,LiveCoin~BLK~BTC,Cryptopia~BLK~FTC,BTC38~BLK~BTC,Bleutrade~BLK~DOGE,TradeSatoshi~BLK~LTC,BitZ~BLK~BTC,CCEDK~BLK~BTC,Bleutrade~BLK~BTC,TradeSatoshi~BLK~DOGE,Cryptopia~BLK~UNO,Poloniex~BLK~BTC,Cryptopia~BLK~ETH,Poloniex~BLK~XMR,Cryptopia~BLK~LTC,Bleutrade~BLK~ETH,CCEDK~BLK~USD,TradeSatoshi~BLK~BTC,Cryptsy~BLK~BTC,CCEDK~BLK~EUR,Jubi~BLK~CNY,BitTrex~BLK~BTC,TuxExchange~BLK~BTC,Cryptopia~BLK~POP', 0),
(4340, 'BLU', 'BlueCoin', '4340-BLU.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://www.bluecoin.io/', 'BlueCoin_info', '<p>BlueCoin (BLU) is a scrypt altcoin that is starts with a PoW phase lasting 100 days - and then switches to Proof of Stake. The block time is 90 seconds and the difficulty retargets every block. The coin is based on Scrypt and the PoS interest rate is set to 3%. There was a 3% premine for bugs, bountie and further development.</p>', NULL, NULL, 500000000.00, NULL, 'Yobit~BLU~DOGE,Yobit~BLU~RUR,CCEX~BLU~USD,CCEX~BLU~DOGE,CCEX~BLU~BTC,Cryptsy~BLU~BTC,Yobit~BLU~USD,LiveCoin~BLU~BTC,CCEX~BLU~LTC,BitTrex~BLU~BTC,Cryptsy~BLU~XRP,LiveCoin~BLU~USD,Yobit~BLU~ETH,Yobit~BLU~WAVES,Yobit~BLU~BTC', 0);
