(4342, 'BOST', 'BoostCoin', '4342-BOST.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', NULL, NULL, '<p>Boostcoin (BOST) claims to be the first hybrid PoW/PoS X13 altcoin. The PoW phase was set to have a block reward of 515 coins per block - a sixty second block target and a total supply of 11.7 million coins. The total supply of coins is limited to 40 million including the PoS phase which has an interest rate of 10% annually. There are continuing rewards from PoS blocks towards the BoostCoin foundation and there was a 1% premine.</p>', NULL, NULL, 40000000.00, NULL, 'CCEX~BOST~DOGE,CCEX~BOST~BTC,Cryptsy~BOST~BTC,CCEX~BOST~LTC,CCEX~BOST~USD,BTC38~BOST~BTC,BTC38~BOST~CNY', 0),
(4343, 'BQC', 'BQCoin', '4343-BQC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://bbqcoin.org/', 'BBQcoinOfficial', '<p>BBQCoin often abbreviated to BBQ or BQC, is a scrypt based blockchain fork of the original bitcoin source code, very similar to litecoin and launched only a short while after Litecoin. BBQcoin provides faster transaction confirmations and uses memory-hard, scrypt-based mining proof-of-work algorithm to target the regular computers and GPUs most people already have. The BBQcoin network is scheduled to produce 88 million currency units.</p>', NULL, NULL, 88000000.00, NULL, 'Coinse~BQC~BTC,BTER~BQC~BTC,BTER~BQC~CNY,Cryptsy~BQC~BTC', 0),
(4345, 'XMY', 'MyriadCoin', '4345-XMY.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://myriadplatform.org/', 'myriadcoin', '<p>Myriad uses five proof of work algorithms for one coin which can be chosen by the user - Scrypt, SHA-256D. QuBit, Skein and Groestl. The coin has a block time of 2.5mins and block halving every 967680 blocks.</p>', NULL, NULL, 2000000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~XMY~DOGE,Cryptopia~XMY~XMR,Poloniex~XMY~BTC,Cryptopia~XMY~FTC,TradeSatoshi~XMY~DOGE,Cexio~XMY~BTC,TradeSatoshi~XMY~LTC,Cryptopia~XMY~DOT,TradeSatoshi~XMY~BTC,Cryptopia~XMY~UNO,BitTrex~XMY~BTC,TradeSatoshi~XMY~BCH,Cryptsy~XMY~BTC,Cryptopia~XMY~LTC,Cryptopia~XMY~BTC', 0),
(4346, 'MOON', 'MoonCoin', '4346-MOON.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', NULL, 'RealMooncoin', '<p>There is one coin for each millimeter of covering distance from the Earth to the Moon. Moon Coin has an increasing block reward reduction range, where in the first 100,000 blocks the reward can be between 0 and 1,000,000 coins, this then drops to 0-600,000 coins for the second 100,000 blocks and so on. After block 384,400 all block rewards are fixed at 29531.</p>', NULL, NULL, 2147483648.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~MOON~XMR,Novaexchange~MOON~KIC,CCEX~MOON~USD,Cryptopia~MOON~BTC,Cryptopia~MOON~LTC,Cryptsy~MOON~XRP,Novaexchange~MOON~LTC,Bleutrade~MOON~DOGE,CCEX~MOON~DOGE,Cryptopia~MOON~DOGE,Cryptsy~MOON~LTC,Bleutrade~MOON~BTC,Cryptopia~MOON~FTC,CCEX~MOON~LTC,Bleutrade~MOON~ETH,Novaexchange~MOON~BTC,Cryptopia~MOON~DOT,Cryptopia~MOON~POP,Novaexchange~MOON~ETH,Cryptopia~MOON~ETH,Cryptopia~MOON~UNO,CCEX~MOON~BTC', 0),
(4347, 'ZET', 'ZetaCoin', '4347-ZET.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://zetacoin.com/', 'zetacoins', '<p>Zetacoin is an open source crypto-currency based on Bitcoin and SHA-256. It has faster transaction times and faster difficulty adjustments. Initial coin mining is 160 million coins, thereafter a yearly inflation of 1 million coins. The transaction speed is 20X faster than that of Bitcoin. The coin can be traded on Bter, Cryptsy and Mintpal.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BTER~ZET~CNY,Bleutrade~ZET~BTC,BitTrex~ZET~BTC,Novaexchange~ZET~ETH,BTER~ZET~BTC,Cryptopia~ZET~LTC,Cryptopia~ZET~XMR,Cryptopia~ZET~BTC,Yobit~ZET~RUR,Novaexchange~ZET~BTC,Yobit~ZET~WAVES,Novaexchange~ZET~DOGE,Cryptopia~ZET~DOGE,Cryptopia~ZET~FTC,Coinse~ZET~BTC,Jubi~ZET~CNY,Bleutrade~ZET~DOGE,Novaexchange~ZET~MOON,Cryptsy~ZET~BTC,Cryptsy~ZET~XRP,Cryptsy~ZET~LTC,Cryptopia~ZET~DOT,Yobit~ZET~DOGE,Yobit~ZET~USD,Yobit~ZET~ETH,Bleutrade~ZET~ETH,Yobit~ZET~BTC,Novaexchange~ZET~LTC,Cryptopia~ZET~UNO', 0),
(4348, 'SXC', 'SexCoin', '4348-SXC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://sexcoin.info/project/', 'SexcoinTeam', '<p>Sexcoin - SXC aims to provide adult content consumers, performers and producers a fast, stable and secure method of accepting micro transactions, protecting their customers privacy and progressing adult retail services into the crypto age. Super blocks are another feature.</p>', NULL, NULL, 250000000.00, NULL, 'Yobit~SXC~DOGE,Cryptopia~SXC~BTC,Yobit~SXC~BTC,Yobit~SXC~USD,Novaexchange~SXC~ETH,Cryptsy~SXC~BTC,Cryptopia~SXC~ETH,Yobit~SXC~ETH,Cryptopia~SXC~UNO,Cryptopia~SXC~DOGE,Cryptsy~SXC~XRP,Cryptopia~SXC~LTC,Novaexchange~SXC~MOON,LiveCoin~SXC~BTC,Cryptopia~SXC~XMR,Cryptsy~SXC~LTC,Cryptopia~SXC~DOT,Yobit~SXC~RUR,Cryptopia~SXC~POP,Cryptopia~SXC~FTC,Yobit~SXC~WAVES,Novaexchange~SXC~BTC', 0),
(4349, 'QTL', 'Quatloo', '4349-QTL.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://quatloos.org/', 'quatloocoin', '<p>Quatloo (QTL) is a Proof of Work scrypty alternative crypto currency. Dificulty retargets every block on a block time of 135 seconds.</p>', NULL, NULL, 100000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~QTL~DOGE,Novaexchange~QTL~LTC,Cryptopia~QTL~LTC,Novaexchange~QTL~ETH,Cryptopia~QTL~DOT,TradeSatoshi~QTL~DOGE,Novaexchange~QTL~DOGE,TradeSatoshi~QTL~LTC,Novaexchange~QTL~MOON,Cryptopia~QTL~POP,Cryptopia~QTL~ETH,BitTrex~QTL~BTC,TradeSatoshi~QTL~BTC,Novaexchange~QTL~BTC,Cryptopia~QTL~UNO,Cryptopia~QTL~FTC,Poloniex~QTL~BTC,Cryptopia~QTL~XMR,Cryptopia~QTL~BTC', 0),
(4350, 'ENRG', 'EnergyCoin', '4350-ENRG.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://energycoin.pw/', 'energycoin', '<p>EnergyCoin (ENRG) is a pure PoS scrypt altcoin with an initial distribution of 110000000 coins going to the 2000 members of the community. The PoS annualised rates drop by 2% per year from 10% to 2% in year 5 - thereafter at year six there is a fixed interest rate of 1% per annum. There is a thirty second block time and a difficulty retargetting each block.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Novaexchange~ENRG~MOON,Novaexchange~ENRG~BTC,Novaexchange~ENRG~KIC,BitTrex~ENRG~BTC,Novaexchange~ENRG~LTC,Novaexchange~ENRG~DOGE', 0),
(4351, 'QRK', 'QuarkCoin', '4351-QRK.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://www.qrk.cc/', 'quarkcoin', '<p>Quark Coin (QRK) Military Grade Encryption and it is a free open source peer-to-peer electronic cash system that is completely decentralized, without the need for a central server or trusted parties. Users hold the crypto keys to their own money and transact directly with each other, with the help of a P2P network to check for double-spending. Super secure hashing: 9 rounds of hashing from 6 hashing functions (blake, bmw, groestl, jh, keccak, skein). 3 rounds apply a random hashing function.</p>', NULL, NULL, 247000000.00, NULL, 'BTER~QRK~CNY,Novaexchange~QRK~BTC,Coinse~QRK~XPM,Novaexchange~QRK~LTC,Novaexchange~QRK~ESP2,Cryptopia~QRK~DOGE,Cryptopia~QRK~XMR,Cryptsy~QRK~XRP,BXinth~QRK~BTC,Cryptopia~QRK~BTC,Cryptopia~QRK~UNO,Cryptsy~QRK~LTC,Coinse~QRK~BTC,Cryptopia~QRK~POP,Novaexchange~QRK~MOON,Cryptsy~QRK~BTC,BTER~QRK~BTC,Coinse~QRK~LTC,BTC38~QRK~CNY,Novaexchange~QRK~ETH,Novaexchange~QRK~DOGE,Cryptopia~QRK~FTC,Cryptopia~QRK~DOT,BTC38~QRK~BTC,Cryptopia~QRK~LTC', 0),
(4352, 'RIC', 'Riecoin', '4352-RIC.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://riecoin.org/', 'riecoin', '<p>Riecoin is in homage to Bernhard Riemann who studied the distribution of prime numbers. RieCoin is a POW altcoin with a blocktime of 2.5 mins and difficulty retagetting every 288 blocks or 12 hours. There is a hard cap of 84 million RIC.</p>', NULL, NULL, 84000000.00, NULL, 'Poloniex~RIC~BTC,BTC38~RIC~CNY', 0),
(4353, 'DGC', 'DigiCoin', '4353-DGC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://digitalcoin.co/', 'DigitalcoinDGC', '<p>Digitalcoin is an alternative open-source cryptocurrency with focus on economic fairness and growth. It uses the tagline "A Currency for the Digital Age". The Digitalcoin community aims to help facilitate the circulation of digital currency by bridging the gap between the common public and the new cryptocurrency technology.</p><p>Blocks are hashed using Scrypt, X11 and SHA256 algorithms. The average block confirmation time for Digitalcoin takes about 40 seconds. The total supply of digitalcoins will balance out around 48,166,000 as block halvings occur.</p>', NULL, NULL, 48166000.00, NULL, 'Novaexchange~DGC~BTC,BitTrex~DGC~BTC,Cryptopia~DGC~DOGE,BTC38~DGC~CNY,Bleutrade~DGC~DOGE,Cryptopia~DGC~ETH,Cryptopia~DGC~DOT,BTER~DGC~BTC,Bleutrade~DGC~ETH,Cryptsy~DGC~XRP,Cryptopia~DGC~LTC,Cryptopia~DGC~FTC,Cryptsy~DGC~LTC,Cryptopia~DGC~XMR,Cryptopia~DGC~BTC,Cryptopia~DGC~UNO,Coinse~DGC~BTC,Novaexchange~DGC~ETH,Bleutrade~DGC~BTC,Cryptsy~DGC~BTC,Novaexchange~DGC~DOGE,BTER~DGC~CNY', 0),
(4354, 'LIMX', 'LimeCoinX', '4354-LIMX.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', NULL, NULL, '<p><span>LimeCoinx (LIMX) is an X11 altcoin that is based on the 11 hashing functions of blake, bmx, groestl, jh, keccak, skein, luffa, cubehash, shavite, simd, and echo. The maximum money supply of LIMX is set to 21 million. The block time is 5 minutes and the difficulty retargets every 36 blocks using the Dark Gravity Wave process. The block reward is 50 coins per block and there was a 2%+ premine.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 21000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~LIMX~UNO,Yobit~LIMX~USD,BitTrex~LIMX~BTC,Yobit~LIMX~BTC,Cryptopia~LIMX~DOGE,Cryptsy~LIMX~BTC,Cryptopia~LIMX~BTC,Yobit~LIMX~RUR,Yobit~LIMX~ETH,Cryptopia~LIMX~LTC,Cryptopia~LIMX~POP,Yobit~LIMX~WAVES,Cryptopia~LIMX~DOT,Yobit~LIMX~DOGE,Cryptopia~LIMX~FTC', 0),
(4371, 'ARG', 'Argentum', '4371-ARG.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', NULL, NULL, '<p>Argentum is another fast block time coin at 32 seconds. It is a scrypt proof of work coin with difficulty retargetting every 250 blocks. The name comes from the Latin for silver and the coin will have a 1.1% annual inflation after the the hard coded total coin cap is reached. The block reward is random and the maximum block size is 10mb.</p>', NULL, NULL, 64000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~ARG~UNO,Novaexchange~ARG~BTC,Novaexchange~ARG~MOON,Cryptopia~ARG~DOGE,Cryptopia~ARG~FTC,Cryptopia~ARG~ETH,Cryptsy~ARG~BTC,Cryptopia~ARG~LTC,Cryptopia~ARG~BTC,Cryptopia~ARG~DOT,Cryptopia~ARG~XMR,Cryptsy~ARG~XRP', 0),
