(4433, 'XVG', 'Verge', '4433-XVG.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://vergecurrency.com/', 'vergecurrency', '<p>Verge is a scrypt based alternative crypto currency trying to take the popularity of both Dogecoin and Bitcoin and combine it with the anonymous features of DASH. The block time is 30 seconds and the coin operates through Proof of Work.</p><p>VERGE prides itself on being a symbol of progression in the cryptocurrency world. It is a more secure, private, and evolving cryptocurrency that is backed by bitcoin, a ton of developer resources and privacy tools (<a href="https://github.com/vergecurrency/" target="_blank">located here</a>!)</p><p><strong>Block reward</strong>:</p><ul><li>Block 0 to 14,000 : 200,000 coins</li><li>14,000 to 28,000 : 100,000 coins</li><li>28,000 to 42,000: 50,000 coins</li><li>42,000 to 210,000: 25,000 coins</li><li>210,000 to 378,000: 12,500 coins</li><li>378,000 to 546,000: 6,250 coins</li><li>546,000 to 714,000: 3,125 coins</li><li>714,000 to 2,124,000: 1,560 coins</li><li>2,124,000 to 4,248,000: 730 coins</li></ul><p><span>Approximately total reward: 9 Billion (9,000,000,000) during first year then issuing 1 billion (1,000,000,000) each year after.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BitTrex~XVG~BTC,Novaexchange~XVG~PIGGY,Cryptopia~XVG~POP,HitBTC~XVG~USD,Yobit~XVG~DOGE,Cryptopia~XVG~XMR,CCEX~XVG~ETH,TradeSatoshi~XVG~BCH,Yobit~XVG~ETH,CCEX~XVG~BTC,Novaexchange~XVG~DOGE,Novaexchange~XVG~LTC,Yobit~XVG~WAVES,CCEX~XVG~DOGE,Cryptopia~XVG~DOT,Cryptopia~XVG~BTC,Yobit~XVG~USD,BitTrex~XVG~USD,TradeSatoshi~XVG~BTC,Binance~XVG~ETH,Cryptopia~XVG~NZDT,TradeSatoshi~XVG~DOGE,Binance~XVG~BTC,Novaexchange~XVG~ETH,Yobit~XVG~BTC,Cryptopia~XVG~LTC,TradeSatoshi~XVG~USDT,Novaexchange~XVG~BTC,HitBTC~XVG~ETH,Cryptopia~XVG~FTC,CCEX~XVG~LTC,Cryptopia~XVG~ETH,Cryptopia~XVG~UNO,TradeSatoshi~XVG~LTC,Yobit~XVG~RUR,Cryptopia~XVG~USDT,Novaexchange~XVG~MOON,Cryptopia~XVG~DOGE,HitBTC~XVG~BTC,CCEX~XVG~USD', 0),
(4434, 'DRKC', 'DarkCash', '4434-DRKC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', NULL, NULL, '<p>DarkCash is another anonymity based crypto currency. The coin has a proof of work phase that produces 3.72 million DRKC units through X11. The subsequent Proof of Stake phase has an annualised 17% rate. </p>', NULL, NULL, 3720000.00, NULL, 'BTER~DRKC~BTC,Cryptsy~DRKC~BTC,Cryptsy~DRKC~XRP', 0),
(4435, 'DSB', 'DarkShibe', '4435-DSB.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=833133.0', 'DarkShibe', '<p>DarkShibe is another crypto currency like Darkcoin - that takes the Dogecoin and Darkcoin elements and fuses them together. The coin is scrypt based and initially operates a proof of work phase that then shifts to a pure proof of stake with an annualised rate at 9%. You can trade DarkShibe for Bitcoin on the exchanges below.</p>', NULL, NULL, 2043962.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~DSB~BTC', 0);
