(4528, 'GLD', 'GoldCoin', '4528-GLD.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://www.gldcoin.com/', 'GoldCoinInfo', '<p>GoldCoin (GLD) is the Gold Standard of Digital Currency - With large vibrant support, trading communities, real world appeal and an extremely devoted development team, GoldCoin is the Gold Standard of Digital Currency. Block time + difficulty changes depending on the height of the block chain along with demarcated block rewards. The GoldCoin team have implemented Golden River - a method to adjust the block time each block to counteract large swings in hashing power pointed at the network - this method is smoother than than the Kimoto Gravity well meaning block times are more closely regulated.</p>', NULL, NULL, 123423904.00, NULL, 'Novaexchange~GLD~BTC,TradeSatoshi~GLD~LTC,Cryptopia~GLD~DOT,Novaexchange~GLD~ETH,CCEX~GLD~USD,Novaexchange~GLD~DOGE,CCEX~GLD~BTC,Cryptopia~GLD~UNO,Cryptopia~GLD~XMR,Cryptsy~GLD~LTC,TradeSatoshi~GLD~BTC,Cryptopia~GLD~FTC,CCEX~GLD~ETH,Cryptopia~GLD~DOGE,Novaexchange~GLD~LTC,Cryptopia~GLD~LTC,CCEX~GLD~LTC,CCEX~GLD~DOGE,Cryptopia~GLD~POP,Cryptsy~GLD~BTC,BitTrex~GLD~BTC,Cryptsy~GLD~XRP,TradeSatoshi~GLD~DOGE,Cryptopia~GLD~BTC', 0),
(4529, 'GLX', 'GalaxyCoin', '4529-GLX.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://galaxy.cryptcoins.net/', NULL, '<p>Galaxycoin (GLX) is a descedant of Novacoin, it uses both Proof of Work and Proof of Stake. It is effectively resistent to 51% attack. There are 64 coins per block and a block target time of 30 seconds. The difficulty retargetting is smoothed based on the last ten blocks average. Mining block rewards need 50 confirmations and transactions need 3 confirmations.</p>', NULL, NULL, 538214400.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~GLX~BTC', 0),
(4530, 'GLYPH', 'GlyphCoin', '4530-GLYPH.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', NULL, NULL, '<p>GlyphCoin (GLYPH) is an X11 PoW PoS alternative crypto currency. The PoS rate is 10% per annum and the block time is 90 seconds per block with difficulty retargetting each block too. There was 0% premine.</p>', NULL, NULL, 7000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~GLYPH~XRP,Coinse~GLYPH~BTC,Cryptsy~GLYPH~BTC,Cryptsy~GLYPH~LTC', 0),
(4531, 'GML', 'GameLeagueCoin', '4531-GML.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=595779.0', 'GameLeaguecoin', '<p>GameLeagueCoin (GLC) is a PoW/PoS crypto currency with a difficulty retargetting every block and a block time of 60 seconds. The coin is scrypt and the POS carries an interest rate of 50% in Y1, 20% Y2, 10% Y3, 5% Y4, 2% Y5 and 1% thereafter. The coin was 100% premined for use in an online game.</p>', NULL, NULL, 500000000.00, NULL, 'Yobit~GML~BTC,Yobit~GML~WAVES,Cryptsy~GML~BTC,Yobit~GML~RUR,Poloniex~GML~BTC,Yobit~GML~ETH,Yobit~GML~DOGE,Yobit~GML~USD,BitTrex~GML~BTC', 0),
