(4536, 'HVC', 'HeavyCoin', '4536-HVC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://heavycoin.github.io/', 'HeavycoinNews', '<p>HeavyCoin is another unique crypto Currency with its Hefty1 algorithm to encourage CPU mining only. The coin is secure due to its SHA-256 Keccak-512, Blake-512 combination. The coin also has pegged difficulty retargetting and a decentralised block reward voting. Otherwise a block time of 2 mins and Kimoto Gravity well temporal retargetting.</p>', NULL, NULL, 128000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~HVC~XRP,Cryptsy~HVC~BTC', 0),
