(4575, 'NMB', 'Nimbus Coin', '4575-NMB.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', NULL, NULL, '<p>Nimbus Coin is an X15 proof of work and proof of stake hybrid - the project has been closed for development due to lack of funding - however the coin can still be traded on cryptsy. The PoS rate is 2%.</p>', NULL, NULL, 25000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~NMB~BTC,Cryptsy~NMB~XRP', 0),
(4576, 'NRB', 'NoirBits', '4576-NRB.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://www.noirbits.com/', 'NoirbitsCoin', '<p>NoirBits (NRB) The 2 minute block time aims to improve on LTC&#39;s time but not so drastic as to cause a permanent orphan problems. There are 50 million total coins with 20 coins per block and a 2 minute block time.There is an hourly retargetting with a 30 block mining confirmation and a six block transaction confirmation.</p>', NULL, NULL, 50000000.00, NULL, 'Coinse~NRB~BTC,Cryptsy~NRB~BTC', 0),
(4577, 'NOBL', 'NobleCoin', '4577-NOBL.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'https://www.noblemovement.com/', 'NobleCoin', '<p>NobleCoin (NBL) is a scrypt based altcoin with a block time of 60 seconds - with five confirmations needed for transactions and 50 required for minting.  The coin supports transaction messaging and difficulty retargets every thirty blocks.</p>', NULL, NULL, 2147483648.00, NULL, 'CCEX~NOBL~BTC,BitTrex~NOBL~BTC,CCEX~NOBL~USD,Cryptopia~NOBL~BTC,Cryptsy~NOBL~BTC,Cryptopia~NOBL~UNO,CCEX~NOBL~DOGE,Poloniex~NOBL~BTC,Cryptopia~NOBL~LTC,Cryptopia~NOBL~DOGE', 0),
(4578, 'NRS', 'NoirShares', '4578-NRS.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', NULL, 'NoirDS', '<p>Noirshares are another interesting concept as a coin as well as being a PoW/PoS coin - they also double as an equity investment for the NIG Group. The coin has a block reward reduction every 3000 blocks and difficulty adjustments each block. There are 80 NRS per block originally and the PoW phase is limited by a hard cap of 5million NRS. Transaction fees are destroyed and taken out of the system to counter the inflation of the PoS stage.</p>', NULL, NULL, 5000000.00, NULL, 'BTC38~NRS~BTC,Cryptsy~NRS~BTC', 0),
(4579, 'NVC', 'NovaCoin', '4579-NVC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://novacoin.org/', 'MarketNvc', '<p>Novacoin is a hybrid scrypt Proof-of-Work + Proof-of-Stake based cryptocurrency operating with no central authority via peer-to-peer open source network. Novacoin has no hard cap except for the 2 billion coin max that has been entered for coding purposes; this can be lifted in the future if needed.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'LiveCoin~NVC~USD,Novaexchange~NVC~LTC,Yobit~NVC~WAVES,Novaexchange~NVC~BTC,CCEX~NVC~USD,CCEX~NVC~LTC,Cryptopia~NVC~POP,Cryptsy~NVC~BTC,Novaexchange~NVC~ETH,Cryptopia~NVC~ETH,Novaexchange~NVC~DOGE,BTCE~NVC~USD,Cryptopia~NVC~DOGE,TradeSatoshi~NVC~DOGE,Bleutrade~NVC~ETH,Yobit~NVC~USD,Coinse~NVC~BTC,TradeSatoshi~NVC~LTC,Cryptsy~NVC~XRP,Cryptopia~NVC~UNO,LiveCoin~NVC~BTC,BTCE~NVC~BTC,TradeSatoshi~NVC~BTC,Yobit~NVC~DOGE,Bleutrade~NVC~BTC,Cryptopia~NVC~XMR,Bleutrade~NVC~DOGE,CCEX~NVC~BTC,Yobit~NVC~ETH,Yobit~NVC~RUR,Cryptopia~NVC~BTC,CCEX~NVC~DOGE,Yobit~NVC~BTC,Cryptopia~NVC~LTC,Cryptopia~NVC~DOT,Cryptopia~NVC~FTC', 0),
(4580, 'NMC', 'NameCoin', '4580-NMC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'https://namecoin.info/', 'Namecoin', '<p>Namecoin s a cryptocurrency which also acts as an alternative, decentralized DNS, which would avoid domain name censorship by making a new top level domain outside of ICANN control. The coin is designed to halve every four years with the same cap limit as Bitcoin of 21,000,000. With the domain registry service a small number of NMC will be destroyed so after mining has finished there will still be a deflationary ellement in place. Namecoin was the first coin to switch to merged mining.</p>', '<ul><li>Namecoin can store data within its own blockchain transaction database</li><li>Censorship-resistant top level domain .bit, which is functionally similar to .com or .net domains but is independent of ICANN, the main governing body for domain names</li><li>Identity systems</li><li>Messaging systems</li><li>Personal namespaces</li><li>Notary/timestamp systems</li><li>Alias systems</li><li>Issuance of shares/stocks</li></ul>', '<p>It is based on the code of bitcoin and uses the same proof-of-work algorithm. It is limited to 21 million coins. Each Namecoin record consists of a key and a value which can be up to 520 bytes in size. Each key is actually a path, with the namespace preceding the name of the record. The key d/example signifies a record stored in the DNS namespace d with the name example and corresponds to the record for the example.bit website. The content of d/example is expected to conform to the DNS namespace specification. The current fee for a record is 0.01 NMC and records expire after 36000 blocks (~200 days) unless updated or renewed. Namecoins used to purchase records are marked as used and destroyed, as giving the fee to miners would enable larger miners to register names at a significant discount.</p>', 21000000.00, NULL, 'BXinth~NMC~BTC,Cryptopia~NMC~ETH,Cryptopia~NMC~DOGE,Cryptopia~NMC~FTC,Yobit~NMC~BTC,Cryptsy~NMC~XRP,BTCE~NMC~BTC,BitSquare~NMC~BTC,Kraken~NMC~BTC,BTER~NMC~CNY,TuxExchange~NMC~BTC,LiveCoin~NMC~BTC,Yobit~NMC~RUR,Bleutrade~NMC~DOGE,Cryptopia~NMC~BTC,BTCE~NMC~USD,Cryptopia~NMC~DOT,Cryptsy~NMC~BTC,Cryptopia~NMC~UNO,Yobit~NMC~ETH,Bleutrade~NMC~BTC,Poloniex~NMC~BTC,Yobit~NMC~DOGE,Bleutrade~NMC~ETH,Cryptopia~NMC~LTC,Yobit~NMC~WAVES,Cexio~NMC~BTC,BTER~NMC~BTC,Yobit~NMC~USD,Cryptopia~NMC~XMR', 0),
(4581, 'NYAN', 'NyanCoin', '4581-NYAN.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://nyancoin.org/', 'Nyan_Coin', '<p>A coin based on a meme of an animated flying cat in the same vein as flappy coin. The algorithm is Scrypt and there are 337 coins per block halving every 337,000 block with a 1% premine for bounties. The block target is set to 1 minute, or 60 seconds, and difficulty retargets every 3 hours.</p>', NULL, NULL, 337000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~NYAN~POP,Novaexchange~NYAN~BTC,Cryptopia~NYAN~XMR,Novaexchange~NYAN~MOON,TradeSatoshi~NYAN~BTC,TradeSatoshi~NYAN~USDT,TradeSatoshi~NYAN~LTC,Cryptsy~NYAN~LTC,Cryptopia~NYAN~BTC,Novaexchange~NYAN~ETH,Cryptopia~NYAN~LTC,Cryptopia~NYAN~FTC,Cryptopia~NYAN~DOT,Cryptopia~NYAN~ETH,Novaexchange~NYAN~LTC,TradeSatoshi~NYAN~DOGE,Novaexchange~NYAN~PIGGY,Cryptopia~NYAN~UNO,Novaexchange~NYAN~DOGE,Cryptopia~NYAN~DOGE,Cryptsy~NYAN~BTC', 0),
(4582, 'OPAL', 'OpalCoin', '4582-OPAL.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://www.opalcoin.com/', 'OpalCoinTeam', '<p>OpalCoin is a rebranding and relaunch of OnyxCoin. The coin is a hybrid proof of work and proof of stake running on X13. The proof of stake rate is 5% per annum.</p>', NULL, NULL, 15000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~OPAL~XMR,Yobit~OPAL~ETH,Cryptsy~OPAL~BTC,Cryptopia~OPAL~BTC,Cryptsy~OPAL~XRP,Poloniex~OPAL~BTC,Cryptopia~OPAL~DOT,Yobit~OPAL~DOGE,Cryptopia~OPAL~UNO,Yobit~OPAL~RUR,Yobit~OPAL~USD,Cryptopia~OPAL~DOGE,Yobit~OPAL~WAVES,Cryptopia~OPAL~LTC,Novaexchange~OPAL~BTC,Yobit~OPAL~BTC,BitTrex~OPAL~BTC', 0),
(4583, 'ORB', 'Orbitcoin', '4583-ORB.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://orbitcoin.org/', 'OrBitcoinLove', '<p>A coin that is a clone but with the added mission of trying to encourage scientific research. OrbitCoin is a PoW/PoS hybrid without the PoS reward to reduce inflation but maintain the resistance to 51% attacks. There are transaction messages with a 30 second block time, a block reward that halves from 0.25 to a minimal 0.00000001. There are four transaction confirmations needed and 200 for newly mined blocks.</p><p><span>block hashing is BLAKE2s</span><br /><span>PoW hashing is NeoScrypt</span><br /><span>PoS hashing is SHA-256d</span></p>', '<ul><li>advanced hybrid proof-of-work (PoW) and proof-of-stake (PoS)</li><li>3.77 million coins to be produced</li><li>block hashing is BLAKE2s</li><li>PoW hashing is NeoScrypt</li><li>PoS hashing is SHA-256d</li><li>1 minute combined block target (3 minutes for PoW, 1.5 minutes for PoS)</li><li>retargets every block using Orbitcoin Super Shield (OSS)</li><li>time warp and instamining protection</li><li>advanced checkpointing against 51% attacks</li><li>transaction messaging supported</li><li>the 1st implementation of 0% PoS</li><li>PoW and PoS blocks carry the same fixed reward of 1 ORB</li><li>6 confirmations for regular transactions</li><li>200 confirmations for minted coins</li><li>very low transaction fees (most transactions are free)</li><li>no destruction of transaction fees (all collected by a block finder)</li><li>the default P2P port is 15298, RPC port is 15299</li><li>I2P/Tor ready</li></ul>', NULL, 3770000.00, NULL, 'Novaexchange~ORB~LTC,Cryptopia~ORB~POP,Cryptopia~ORB~DOGE,Cryptsy~ORB~XRP,TradeSatoshi~ORB~LTC,Novaexchange~ORB~ETH,Coinse~ORB~LTC,TradeSatoshi~ORB~BCH,Cryptopia~ORB~DOT,BitTrex~ORB~BTC,Cryptopia~ORB~ETH,TradeSatoshi~ORB~DOGE,TradeSatoshi~ORB~BTC,Coinse~ORB~BTC,Cryptopia~ORB~FTC,Novaexchange~ORB~DOGE,Cryptopia~ORB~LTC,Novaexchange~ORB~BTC,Cryptopia~ORB~UNO,Cryptopia~ORB~XMR,Cryptopia~ORB~BTC,Cryptsy~ORB~BTC', 0),
(4584, 'OSC', 'OpenSourceCoin', '4584-OSC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=268705.0', NULL, '<p>OpenSourceCoin (OSC) it is different from other cryptocurrencies due to its innovative features like symmetrically scaling difficulty retarget algorithm and its is a SHA 256 POW/POS cryptocurrency.</p>', NULL, NULL, 21000000.00, NULL, 'Novaexchange~OSC~BTC,Cryptopia~OSC~BTC,Cryptopia~OSC~LTC,Novaexchange~OSC~ETH,Cryptsy~OSC~XRP,Cryptopia~OSC~DOT,Cryptopia~OSC~FTC,Cryptsy~OSC~BTC,Cryptopia~OSC~UNO,Cryptopia~OSC~POP,Cryptopia~OSC~DOGE', 0),
(4585, 'PHS', 'PhilosophersStone', '4585-PHS.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://phstones.com/', NULL, '<p>Philosopherstone provides an annual interest rate of 50%, for stakes that are not moved during the period. This equivalent to 3.44% monthly interest. PoS blocks will be generated if the stake is held for more than 5 days.</p>', NULL, NULL, 8891840.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~PHS~DOGE,Cryptsy~PHS~XRP,Cryptopia~PHS~LTC,Cryptopia~PHS~UNO,Cryptopia~PHS~POP,Cryptopia~PHS~XMR,Cryptopia~PHS~BTC,Cryptopia~PHS~FTC,Cryptsy~PHS~BTC,Cryptopia~PHS~DOT,Cryptopia~PHS~ETH', 0),
(4586, 'POINTS', 'Cryptsy Points', '4586-POINTS.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://www.cryptsy.com', 'cryptsy', '<p>Cryptsy Points are the cryptsy exchanges own internal affiliate refferal program currency. No algorithm and no code. Cryptsy calculates its payouts every day for your activity.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Cryptsy~POINTS~BTC', 0),
(4587, 'POT', 'PotCoin', '4587-POT.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://www.potcoin.cc/', 'PotCoin', '<p>PotCoin is another scrypt coin launched at the start of 2014. PotCoin is supposed to empower and facilitate the marijuana industry. The first 55 blocks were premined for checkpoints - and the coin has a relatively fast blocktime of 40 seconds.</p>', NULL, NULL, 420000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~POT~BTC,Cryptopia~POT~FTC,Poloniex~POT~BTC,Bleutrade~POT~DOGE,TradeSatoshi~POT~DOGE,TuxExchange~POT~BTC,Cryptopia~POT~LTC,Bleutrade~POT~ETH,Cexio~POT~BTC,TradeSatoshi~POT~LTC,Cryptsy~POT~XRP,Cryptopia~POT~POP,Cryptopia~POT~ETH,Cryptopia~POT~DOGE,Cryptopia~POT~XMR,Novaexchange~POT~ETH,TradeSatoshi~POT~BCH,Cryptopia~POT~DOT,Bleutrade~POT~BTC,Cryptsy~POT~BTC,BitTrex~POT~BTC,Novaexchange~POT~BTC,TradeSatoshi~POT~BTC,Cryptopia~POT~UNO,Novaexchange~POT~LTC', 0),
(4588, 'PSEUD', 'PseudoCash', '4588-PSEUD.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', NULL, NULL, '<p>PseudoCash (PSEUD) is an X13 crypto currency. The proof of stake is set to 5% per annum. </p>', NULL, NULL, 2200000.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~PSEUD~BTC', 0),
(4589, 'PTS*', 'Protoshares', '4589-PTS.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'https://bitsharestalk.org/index.php?board=1.0', 'protoshares', '<p>Protoshares are a confusing alt coin (any cryptocurrency that isn&#39;t Bitcoin). They&#39;re not just another cryptocurrency, though they are mined and can be traded like conventional crypto. Beyond that, they also represent shares in Invictus-Innovation&#39;s cryptocurrencies and digital creations.</p>', NULL, NULL, 2000000.00, NULL, 'CCEX~PTS*~BTC,BTER~PTS*~CNY,Poloniex~PTS*~BTC,Coinse~PTS*~BTC,CCEX~PTS*~DOGE,CCEX~PTS*~USD,CCEX~PTS*~LTC,Cryptsy~PTS*~XRP,Cryptsy~PTS*~BTC,BTER~PTS*~BTC', 0),
(4590, 'PXC', 'PhoenixCoin', '4590-PXC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://phoenixcoin.org/', 'Phoenixcoin', '<p>Phoenixcoin (PXC)is Scrypt based cryptocoin and digital currency for everyone. It doesn&#39;t depend upon very expensive hardware and can be mined successfully with popular computer video cards or processors. It is also a fast and reliable way to send money worldwide. The currency can be used on the developers casino website.</p>', NULL, NULL, 98000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~PXC~XMR,Cryptsy~PXC~XRP,Cryptopia~PXC~FTC,Cryptsy~PXC~LTC,Cryptopia~PXC~UNO,Cryptopia~PXC~BTC,Cryptopia~PXC~LTC,Cryptopia~PXC~POP,Cryptopia~PXC~DOGE,Cryptsy~PXC~BTC', 0),
(4591, 'PYC', 'PayCoin', '4591-PYC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', NULL, NULL, '<p>PayCoin is a peer-to-peer (P2P) Internet currency that enables instant payments to anyone in the world. It runs off the popular scrypt protocol which gives it unmatched stability and easy accessibility. PayCoin uses memory-hard, scrypt-based mining with both proof-of-work and proof of stake algorithm to target the regular computers and GPUs most people already have.</p>', NULL, NULL, 30000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~PYC~BTC', 0),
(4592, 'RDD', 'ReddCoin', '4592-RDD.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'https://www.reddcoin.com/', 'reddcoin', '<p>ReddCoin is trying to jump on the tipping bandwagon by making itself the social network donation go to default. A Scrypt coin with a 60 second block time and block retargeting using kimoto&#39;s gravity well. The coin also includes a 5% annual inflation after the 27.5 billion have been mined by PoW. Alongside Reddcoin inludes an innovative proof of stake velocity algorithm.</p>', NULL, NULL, 2147483648.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~RDD~LTC,Novaexchange~RDD~KIC,Cryptopia~RDD~FTC,Cryptopia~RDD~UNO,Cryptopia~RDD~XMR,Poloniex~RDD~BTC,Bleutrade~RDD~DOGE,Yobit~RDD~RUR,Yobit~RDD~WAVES,Cryptopia~RDD~DOT,Yobit~RDD~BTC,TradeSatoshi~RDD~LTC,Novaexchange~RDD~ESP2,Novaexchange~RDD~LTC,TradeSatoshi~RDD~BCH,Cryptsy~RDD~XRP,Cryptsy~RDD~BTC,Yobit~RDD~ETH,Novaexchange~RDD~BTC,Yobit~RDD~DOGE,Novaexchange~RDD~DOGE,Cryptopia~RDD~DOGE,TradeSatoshi~RDD~USDT,BitSquare~RDD~BTC,Bleutrade~RDD~ETH,Novaexchange~RDD~ETH,Yobit~RDD~USD,TradeSatoshi~RDD~DOGE,Cryptopia~RDD~LTC,Novaexchange~RDD~PIGGY,Cryptopia~RDD~POP,Bleutrade~RDD~BTC,TradeSatoshi~RDD~BTC,Cryptopia~RDD~BTC,BitTrex~RDD~BTC,Cryptopia~RDD~ETH,Cryptsy~RDD~USD', 0),
(4593, 'RIPO', 'RipOffCoin', '4593-RIPO.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', NULL, 'RipoffCoin', '<p>A crypto currency that mocks the numerous others that are actually scams. For example stating there was no premine then that there in fact was a hidden premine. A scrypt coin with roughly 12 milllion RIPO. </p>', NULL, NULL, 12000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~RIPO~BTC,Coinse~RIPO~BTC', 0),
(4594, 'RPC', 'RonPaulCoin', '4594-RPC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://www.ronpaulcoin.com/', 'RPCoin', '<p>RonPaulCoin, or RPC, has a hard-coded cap of only 2.1 million coins that will come into existence. This is significantly lower than Bitcoin, which has 21 million total coins.</p>', NULL, NULL, 21000000.00, NULL, 'Yobit~RPC~BTC,Yobit~RPC~DOGE,Yobit~RPC~ETH,Cryptopia~RPC~DOT,Yobit~RPC~WAVES,Cryptopia~RPC~UNO,Cryptopia~RPC~LTC,Yobit~RPC~RUR,Cryptopia~RPC~FTC,Cryptopia~RPC~DOGE,Cryptopia~RPC~BTC,Yobit~RPC~USD,Cryptopia~RPC~XMR,Cryptsy~RPC~BTC', 0),
