(4627, 'TTC', 'TittieCoin', '4627-TTC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://tittiecoin.com/', 'TittieCoin', '<p>TittieCoin is another coin attempting to sync up with the erotic industries - a scrypt proof of work crypto currency.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~TTC~LTC,Novaexchange~TTC~DOGE,Cryptopia~TTC~FTC,Novaexchange~TTC~ESP2,Novaexchange~TTC~ETH,Yobit~TTC~BTC,Cryptopia~TTC~DOT,Yobit~TTC~WAVES,Cryptopia~TTC~XMR,Yobit~TTC~DOGE,Cryptopia~TTC~POP,Novaexchange~TTC~BTC,Cryptopia~TTC~UNO,Yobit~TTC~ETH,Yobit~TTC~RUR,Cryptopia~TTC~BTC,Cryptsy~TTC~BTC,Cryptopia~TTC~DOGE,Yobit~TTC~USD,Novaexchange~TTC~MOON', 0),
(4628, 'ULTC', 'Umbrella', '4628-ULTC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://www.umbrella.holdings/', NULL, '<p>Umbrella coins and its alternatives are an attempt at insuring against exchange loss or wallet key loss. Otherwise the coin is made as a pair to the major crypto currency of each algorithm type. This is the SHA-256 version. </p>', NULL, NULL, 2625000.00, NULL, 'Poloniex~ULTC~BTC,Cryptsy~ULTC~BTC,BitTrex~ULTC~BTC', 0),
(4629, 'UNB', 'UnbreakableCoin', '4629-UNB.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://www.unbreakablecoin.com/', 'Unbreakablcoin', '<p>Unbreakable Coin is a SHA-256 POW coin with a hard capped limit of 80 million UNB and a block time of 300 seconds. There is a two step block reward with 50 coins for the first 800,000 blocks and 25 thereafter.</p>', NULL, NULL, 80000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~UNB~UNO,BitTrex~UNB~BTC,CCEX~UNB~LTC,Cryptopia~UNB~DOGE,Cryptopia~UNB~BTC,CCEX~UNB~DOGE,Cryptopia~UNB~DOT,Cryptsy~UNB~BTC,Cryptopia~UNB~LTC,CCEX~UNB~BTC,Cryptopia~UNB~XMR,Cryptsy~UNB~XRP,Cryptopia~UNB~FTC,CCEX~UNB~USD', 0),
(4630, 'UNO', 'Unobtanium', '4630-UNO.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://unobtanium.uno/', 'bryceweiner', '<p>Ultra rarity is this token&#39;s modus operandi. 1 Un per block, halving every 102,000 blocks. Only 196,875 Proof of Work UNOs will be minted before 0.0001 minimum block subsidies take effect at block 612,000. Zero coins premined. UNO&#39;s are an SHA-256 POW coin with a block target of three minutes and a hard cap to the coin supply of 250,000.</p>', NULL, NULL, 250000.00, NULL, 'TradeSatoshi~UNO~LTC,Cryptopia~UNO~DOT,Bleutrade~UNO~ETH,CCEX~UNO~BTC,TradeSatoshi~UNO~BCH,Cryptsy~UNO~XRP,Cryptopia~UNO~USDT,Cryptopia~UNO~DOGE,Cryptopia~UNO~POP,Cryptopia~UNO~FTC,Cryptsy~UNO~BTC,TradeSatoshi~UNO~DOGE,Coinse~UNO~BTC,Cryptopia~UNO~BTC,CCEX~UNO~USD,CCEX~UNO~DOGE,BitTrex~UNO~BTC,Bleutrade~UNO~BTC,Cryptopia~UNO~ETH,BitSquare~UNO~BTC,Cryptopia~UNO~LTC,CCEX~UNO~LTC,TradeSatoshi~UNO~USDT,TradeSatoshi~UNO~BTC,Bleutrade~UNO~DOGE', 0),
(4631, 'URO', 'UroCoin', '4631-URO.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://uro.io/', 'UroFoundation', '<p>UroCoin (URO) is an X11 PoW based alternative crypto currency. Uro&#39;s focus is to try and provide a means for efficient international trade of Urea - they wish to provide a backing to the coins market capitalisation by holding Urea itself. The coin has a block time of 3 minutes and retargets using the safe gravity well. There was no premine and the recommended transaction fee is 0.1%. The total coin supply will be 1 million URO in the first six months and then 10% growth per annum to coincide with the projected growth rate of the global Urea market - as such the block reward will drop from 12 URO after the first six months to 1 URO per block in perpetuity.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yobit~URO~DOGE,Yobit~URO~USD,Yobit~URO~RUR,Yobit~URO~WAVES,Poloniex~URO~BTC,BitTrex~URO~BTC,Cryptsy~URO~BTC,Yobit~URO~ETH,Yobit~URO~BTC,Cryptsy~URO~XRP', 0),
(5011, 'USDE', 'UnitaryStatus Dollar', '5011-USDE.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://www.usde.com/', 'CoinUSDE', '<p>USDe is another scrypt crypto currency - branding itself as an anti establishmentarian - anti Fed - and pro liberty in the American sense. The coin has two block reward reductions when 1/3 of supply has been mined. Total supply is 1.6bn. The coin is scrypt (anti asic mining) with single block difficulty retargetting using the kimoto gravity well. Inital block reward is set at 4000.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1600000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptsy~USDE~XRP,Yobit~USDE~ETH,Yobit~USDE~RUR,Yobit~USDE~BTC,Yobit~USDE~DOGE,Cexio~USDE~BTC,Yobit~USDE~USD,Yobit~USDE~WAVES,Cryptsy~USDE~BTC', 0),
(5012, 'UTC', 'UltraCoin', '5012-UTC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://ultracoin.net/', 'official_utc', '<p>UltraCoin(UTC) uses Scrypt-Jane algorithm, which ensures it cannot be mined by ASICs like other cryptocurrencies as it is released in a transparent process that allows for independent verification of binaries and their corresponding source code, and hybrid proof-of-work / proof-of-stake coin whereby active nodes are involved in the mining of blocks if they maintain a UTC balance. Difficulty retargeting is limited to 200% increases at each retargeting.</p>', NULL, NULL, 100000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~UTC~BTC,Cryptopia~UTC~DOT,Cryptopia~UTC~DOGE,Yacuna~UTC~BTC,Cryptsy~UTC~BTC,Cryptopia~UTC~LTC,Cryptsy~UTC~XRP,BitTrex~UTC~BTC', 0),
(5013, 'UTIL', 'Utility Coin', '5013-UTIL.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', NULL, 'UtilityCoinTeam', '<p>Utility coin is an X13 proof of work and proof of stake hybrid. The proof of stake rate is set to 20% per annum.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Cryptsy~UTIL~BTC,BitTrex~UTIL~BTC', 0),
(5014, 'VDO', 'VidioCoin', '5014-VDO.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://www.vidioshare.me/', 'vidioshare', '<p>VDO is a new video sharing website based on the founding principle of Bitcoin, a new decentralized monetization protocol and video sharing website. One of the most prominent points surrounding the project is the sharing of rewards with video creators and users. Vidio is designed to give users an alternative platform to upload and distribute content across the Internet. Vidio specializes in video platforms and video usability. Vidio will also be built around the Vidio crypto currency. One of the most important features of the service however is that it is completely advertisement free. Instead of gaining outside advertisement revenue intrinsic revenue is provided to all users through decentralized monetization protocol for videos creators and users.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BitTrex~VDO~BTC,Cryptsy~VDO~BTC', 0),
(5015, 'VIA', 'ViaCoin', '5015-VIA.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://viacoin.org/', 'viacoin', '<p>Viacoin is a digital currency similar to Bitcoin that allows the creation of applications on top of the Viacoin blockchain in a similar way that email and web are built on top of the internet protocol. This allows the building of fully decentralized exchanges, issuing of new currencies, asset tracking, betting, digital voting, reputation management and even form the basis of fully decentralized market places. Our protocol for this will be called ClearingHouse.</p>', NULL, NULL, 92000000.00, NULL, 'Binance~VIA~BNB,Novaexchange~VIA~BTC,Binance~VIA~BTC,Novaexchange~VIA~LTC,BitTrex~VIA~BTC,BTER~VIA~BTC,Yobit~VIA~USD,Yobit~VIA~BTC,Cryptsy~VIA~BTC,Yobit~VIA~RUR,Yobit~VIA~DOGE,Yobit~VIA~ETH,Poloniex~VIA~BTC,Cryptsy~VIA~XRP,Binance~VIA~ETH,Yobit~VIA~WAVES,Novaexchange~VIA~ETH', 0),
(5016, 'VOOT', 'VootCoin', '5016-VOOT.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://www.vootcoin.net/', 'vootcoin', '<p>VootCoin is a hybid proof of work and proof of stake alternative crypto currency with a 10% annualised rate.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BTC38~VOOT~BTC,Cryptsy~VOOT~BTC', 0),
(5017, 'VRC', 'VeriCoin', '5017-VRC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://www.vericoin.info/', 'VeriCoin', '<p>VRC is designed to reduce the PoW phase and enter PoS phase quickly. With a steady block reward and block time of sixty seconds, the PoW phase is designed to finish after the first few weeks of launch - 10/05/2014. The PoS interest rate is dynamic and depends on how much the coin is held and staked in the PoS. The dynamic interest rate is pegged at a sensible level of between 0-3% roughly. The PoS interest is gained through transaction fees which are also distributed to the Vericoin fund - to aid in development and promotion of the currency. There was no premine.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Cryptopia~VRC~BTC,TradeSatoshi~VRC~DOGE,Cryptsy~VRC~XRP,Bleutrade~VRC~BTC,Cryptsy~VRC~BTC,Cryptopia~VRC~POP,Cryptopia~VRC~ETH,TradeSatoshi~VRC~BTC,BTER~VRC~CNY,Cryptopia~VRC~DOT,Cryptsy~VRC~LTC,Cryptopia~VRC~FTC,Jubi~VRC~CNY,Bleutrade~VRC~ETH,BitTrex~VRC~BTC,Bleutrade~VRC~DOGE,Cryptopia~VRC~XMR,BTER~VRC~BTC,Cryptopia~VRC~UNO,LiveCoin~VRC~BTC,TradeSatoshi~VRC~LTC,Coinse~VRC~BTC,Cryptopia~VRC~DOGE,Cryptopia~VRC~LTC,Poloniex~VRC~BTC', 0),
(5018, 'VTC', 'Vertcoin', '5018-VTC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'https://vertcoin.org/', 'Vertcoin', '<p>VertCoin (VTC) is a cryptographic currency, similar to Bitcoin and Litecoin, with one major difference - Vertcoin believes that everyone who has personal computer should be able to join the Vertcoin network.</p><p>VertCoin is a Litecoin Fork, that in turn is a Bitcoin Fork.</p><p><span>Vertcoin is also the first cryptocurrency to implement Stealth Addresses, a new technology for providing privacy on the public ledger.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 84000000.00, NULL, 'Bleutrade~VTC~BTC,Cryptsy~VTC~XRP,Yobit~VTC~WAVES,Yobit~VTC~USD,Yobit~VTC~BTC,Bleutrade~VTC~DOGE,BTER~VTC~BTC,Cryptsy~VTC~LTC,Jubi~VTC~CNY,Yobit~VTC~ETH,Poloniex~VTC~BTC,Bleutrade~VTC~ETH,BTER~VTC~CNY,Yobit~VTC~RUR,BitTrex~VTC~BTC,Cryptsy~VTC~BTC,Yobit~VTC~DOGE', 0),
(5019, 'WC', 'WhiteCoin', '5019-WC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://www.whitecoinfoundation.org/', 'WhiteCoiner', '<p>WhiteCoin is a scypt based altcoin that morphs from a PoW into a PoS mode after block 100. Block time is reasonable at 90 seconds and difficulty retargets every block.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Cryptopia~WC~DOGE,Cryptopia~WC~BTC,Cryptopia~WC~LTC,Coinse~WC~BTC,Cryptsy~WC~XRP,Cryptsy~WC~BTC', 0),
(5020, 'WDC', 'WorldCoin', '5020-WDC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://www.worldcoinalliance.net/', 'worldcoin_dach', '<p>WorldCoin is designed to be the digital currency of the future. WorldCoin runs off the popular scrypt protocol which enables it to have stability for early adapters and users by operating from regular existing computer hardware. At the forefront is speed with transactions fully confirmed in about 60 seconds or less.</p>', NULL, NULL, 265420800.00, NULL, 'BTER~WDC~BTC,TradeSatoshi~WDC~LTC,Poloniex~WDC~BTC,BTC38~WDC~CNY,Cryptopia~WDC~XMR,Cryptopia~WDC~LTC,Cryptopia~WDC~BTC,BTC38~WDC~BTC,Novaexchange~WDC~BTC,Cryptopia~WDC~POP,Cexio~WDC~LTC,Coinse~WDC~BTC,Cexio~WDC~BTC,Cryptopia~WDC~ETH,Bleutrade~WDC~ETH,Cryptopia~WDC~FTC,Cryptsy~WDC~XRP,TradeSatoshi~WDC~DOGE,Novaexchange~WDC~LTC,Cryptsy~WDC~BTC,Bleutrade~WDC~DOGE,Novaexchange~WDC~DOGE,Cryptopia~WDC~DOGE,Bleutrade~WDC~BTC,Cryptopia~WDC~UNO,Cryptsy~WDC~LTC,Jubi~WDC~CNY,Cryptopia~WDC~DOT,Novaexchange~WDC~MOON,TradeSatoshi~WDC~BTC,BTER~WDC~CNY', 0),
(5021, 'XAI', 'SapienceCoin', '5021-XAI.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoB/PoS', 'http://www.blockchainsingularity.com/', 'SapienceAIFX', '<p>Fractal Coin intends to distribute 90% of its 1 million coins in the initial 28 days of mining. The coin features a new difficulty adjustment mechanism known as slingshot - the aim of which is to increase the % of controlled hashrate required for a 51% attack to over 70%. The idea is that block rewards will be based solely on transaction fees. Otherwise the coin has a 6o second block time and has a 0.5% premine.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Cryptsy~XAI~BTC,BitTrex~XAI~BTC,Poloniex~XAI~BTC,EtherDelta~XAI~ETH', 0);
