(5383, 'GAIA', 'GAIA Platform', '5383-GAIA.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoS', NULL, 'gaia_coin', '<p>GAIA coin offers the security and reliability of the blockchain with an Extensible, Skinnable, Modular platform design with capabilities to implement distributed markets and services.</p>', NULL, NULL, 24000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~GAIA~POP,Cryptopia~GAIA~DOT,Cryptopia~GAIA~XMR,Cryptopia~GAIA~BTC,Cryptopia~GAIA~UNO,BitTrex~GAIA~BTC,Cryptopia~GAIA~FTC,Cryptopia~GAIA~DOGE,Cryptopia~GAIA~LTC', 0),
(5384, 'TRUST', 'TrustPlus', '5384-TRUST.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://trustplus.co/', NULL, '<p>TrustPlus (TRUST) is an X11 algorithm based crypto currency that has a short PoW phase of just under seven days. The PoS rate is 18% per annum and there was a premine for roughly 10% of the PoW mined coins.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BitTrex~TRUST~BTC', 0),
(5385, 'FCN', 'FantomCoin', '5385-FCN.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', NULL, NULL, '<p>FantomNightCoin (FCN) is a CryptoNight algorithm based coin which is a 64-bit CPU only mineable coin. There is a block time of sixty seconds and the block reward is controlled by a formula that decreases depending on the supply mined to date. The coin retargets every block.</p>', NULL, NULL, 18400000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~FCN~ETH,Cryptopia~FCN~FTC,Cryptopia~FCN~UNO,HitBTC~FCN~BTC,Cryptopia~FCN~XMR,Cryptopia~FCN~BTC,Cryptopia~FCN~LTC,Cryptopia~FCN~DOGE,Cryptopia~FCN~DOT', 0),
(5386, 'XCN', 'Cryptonite', '5386-XCN.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://cryptonite.info/', 'CryptoniteCoin', '<p>Cryptonite was developed by the Mini-blockchain Project over a period of almost four months. Cryptonite is a fork of the Bitcoin core but the code has been extensively modified and expanded upon.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1840000000.00, NULL, 'BTC38~XCN~BTC,Novaexchange~XCN~ETH,Novaexchange~XCN~DOGE,Novaexchange~XCN~KIC,BTER~XCN~BTC,Novaexchange~XCN~LTC,BXinth~XCN~BTC,Novaexchange~XCN~BTC,BTC38~XCN~CNY,Poloniex~XCN~BTC', 0),
(5387, 'CURE', 'Curecoin', '5387-CURE.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'https://www.curecoin.net/', 'CureCoin_Team', '<p>Curecoin is a PoW PoS hybrid altcoin that allows both ASIC mining and CPU &amp; GPU mining to play a part in creating coins - as they call it mining and folding. The added benefit behind the coin is that computer power is used to test protein folding and create a valuable scientific knowledge base. Block halving occurs every million blocks and the block time is 60 seconds.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Poloniex~CURE~BTC,BitTrex~CURE~BTC,LiveCoin~CURE~BTC', 0),
(5388, 'GMC', 'Gridmaster', '5388-GMC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://gridmaster.co/', NULL, '<p><span>Gridmaster Coin (GMC) is a peer to peer crypto currency that is built with the latest technologies in crypto currency such as Dynamic Proof of Stake, Anonymous transactions, Masternodes and Encrypted Messaging. Further developments will focus on building platforms and utilities that bridge the merchant-consumer gap whilst enabling the wider audience to use the digital currency in their everyday lives.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 84000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~GMC~POP,Cryptsy~GMC~BTC,Cryptopia~GMC~BTC,CCEX~GMC~USD,Cryptopia~GMC~FTC,Poloniex~GMC~BTC,Cryptopia~GMC~UNO,BitTrex~GMC~BTC,Cryptopia~GMC~DOT,CCEX~GMC~BTC,CCEX~GMC~DOGE,Cryptopia~GMC~DOGE,Cryptopia~GMC~LTC', 0),
(5389, 'MMC', 'MemoryCoin', '5389-MMC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://memorycoin.org/', NULL, '<p>MemoryCoin (MEM) is a POW is a modified momentum based algorithm and decentralizes currency mining. Each hash requires 1GB of Memory to perform and encrypts 50GB of data. By contrast, the verification only requires 128K and less than one 10th of a second. The coin is inflationary with a rate of 2% after the first two years of mining 10000000 coins.</p>', NULL, NULL, 10000000.00, NULL, 'Novaexchange~MMC~DOGE,BTER~MMC~BTC,Poloniex~MMC~BTC,BTER~MMC~CNY', 0),
(5391, 'XBC', 'BitcoinPlus', '5391-XBC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', NULL, 'BitcoinPlusXBC', '<p>Bitcoin Plus is a Bitcoin advance adding features such as proof of stake with a 10% annnualised interest rate.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'TradeSatoshi~XBC~BTC,Cryptopia~XBC~BTC,Cryptopia~XBC~DOGE,Novaexchange~XBC~DOGE,Cryptopia~XBC~DOT,Cryptopia~XBC~LTC,Cryptopia~XBC~UNO,Poloniex~XBC~BTC,TradeSatoshi~XBC~DOGE,TradeSatoshi~XBC~USDT,TradeSatoshi~XBC~LTC,TradeSatoshi~XBC~BCH,Cryptopia~XBC~XMR,Novaexchange~XBC~MOON,Cryptopia~XBC~FTC,Novaexchange~XBC~BTC', 0),
(5392, 'CYC', 'ConSpiracy Coin', '5392-CYC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', NULL, NULL, '<p>There is no longer a functional website for this crypto currency - although the coin has 33 million total units to be mined by proof of work and X11.</p>', NULL, NULL, 33000000.00, NULL, 'TradeSatoshi~CYC~LTC,Yobit~CYC~ETH,Yobit~CYC~BTC,Poloniex~CYC~BTC,Yobit~CYC~DOGE,TradeSatoshi~CYC~BCH,Yobit~CYC~WAVES,Yobit~CYC~RUR,Yobit~CYC~USD,TradeSatoshi~CYC~BTC,TradeSatoshi~CYC~DOGE', 0),
(5393, 'OCTO', 'OctoCoin', '5393-OCTO.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'http://www.theoctoparty.com/', 'theoctoparty', '<p>OCTO is a Counterparty asset with focus on decentralized website payments for Counterparty assets and Token Control Access Marketing. OCTO will create and fairly distribute a total of 88.8 million coins to be used for early access and testing of the OCTO projects. Distribution includes an alt coin burn, merged mining with FoldingCoin and a future crowd sale.</p>', NULL, NULL, 88000000.00, NULL, 'BitTrex~OCTO~BTC', 0),
