(24854, 'ZEC', 'ZCash', '24854-ZEC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'https://z.cash/', 'zcashco', '<p>ZCash is a privacy driven cryptocurrency. It uses the <strong>Equihash</strong><span> as an algorithm, which is an asymmetric memory-hard Proof of Work algorithm based on the generalized birthday problem. It relies on high RAM requirements to bottleneck the generation of proofs and making ASIC development unfeasible. </span></p><p><span>ZCash uses  zero-knowledge Succinct Non-interactive Arguments of Knowledge (zk-SNARKs) to ensure that all information (sender, reciever, ammount) is encrypted, without the possibility of double-spending. The only information that is revealed regarding transactions is the time in which they take place.</span></p><p><span>Block explorer data from <a href="https://explorer.zcha.in/" target="_blank">https://explorer.zcha.in/</a></span></p>', NULL, NULL, 21000000.00, NULL, 'HuobiPro~ZEC~USDT,Bitfinex~ZEC~USD,Binance~ZEC~ETH,Gateio~ZEC~BTC,WavesDEX~ZEC~WAVES,Bithumb~ZEC~KRW,BitTrex~ZEC~USD,Kraken~ZEC~BTC,OKEX~ZEC~ETH,Yobit~ZEC~WAVES,TradeSatoshi~ZEC~BCH,HuobiPro~ZEC~BTC,Exmo~ZEC~BTC,BitTrex~ZEC~BTC,WavesDEX~ZEC~BCH,BitTrex~ZEC~ETH,Gateio~ZEC~USDT,TradeSatoshi~ZEC~LTC,HitBTC~ZEC~ETH,WavesDEX~ZEC~EUR,Bitfinex~ZEC~BTC,Cryptopia~ZEC~UNO,CCEX~ZEC~USD,Yobit~ZEC~ETH,WavesDEX~ZEC~USD,OKEX~ZEC~USDT,WavesDEX~ZEC~RBX,Poloniex~ZEC~BTC,Cexio~ZEC~USD,Exmo~ZEC~RUB,Kraken~ZEC~EUR,Poloniex~ZEC~USD,Cexio~ZEC~GBP,OKEX~ZEC~BTC,Cexio~ZEC~BTC,HitBTC~ZEC~BTC,TradeSatoshi~ZEC~DOGE,Kraken~ZEC~USD,Cryptopia~ZEC~USDT,Cryptopia~ZEC~XMR,TradeSatoshi~ZEC~BTC,Cryptopia~ZEC~DOT,Cryptopia~ZEC~LTC,WavesDEX~ZEC~MRT,Cryptopia~ZEC~NZDT,BTER~ZEC~CNY,Cryptopia~ZEC~DOGE,TheRockTrading~ZEC~BTC,Yobit~ZEC~DOGE,Abucoins~ZEC~BTC,Poloniex~ZEC~XMR,BitZ~ZEC~BTC,Kraken~ZEC~JPY,TuxExchange~ZEC~BTC,BXinth~ZEC~BTC,Yobit~ZEC~USD,Yobit~ZEC~BTC,TheRockTrading~ZEC~EUR,HitBTC~ZEC~USD,Yunbi~ZEC~CNY,Exmo~ZEC~EUR,WavesDEX~ZEC~WTRY,Poloniex~ZEC~ETH,CC