(26121, 'RBIT', 'ReturnBit', '26121-RBIT.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'http://www.returnbit.com/', 'ReturnBit', '<p>ReturnBit is an investment platform that uses blockchain to reward users via a trust fund dubbed rTrust. The rTrust gets its funds from the block rewards, from which 50% is allocated to it, and from the transaction fees that are generated from RBIT transactions. Users can then, send RBIT to the special rTrust address.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yobit~RBIT~WAVES,Yobit~RBIT~BTC,Yobit~RBIT~USD,Yobit~RBIT~RUR,Yobit~RBIT~ETH,Yobit~RBIT~DOGE', 0),
(26129, 'DCS.', 'deCLOUDs', '26129-DCS.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoS', 'http://www.declouds.com/', 'decloudscom', '<p><strong>Previous information:</strong></p><p>deCLOUDs is a decentralized cloud-based crypto platform that allows users to issue assets and tokens and to exchange them on a peer-to-peer basis. deCLOUDs&#39; system groups nodes into virtual clouds by geographic location and ping time to make interaction between all members ion platform faster and more efficient. deCLOUDs allows asset-to-asset and cross token exchange and it can be acessed via light client, meaning that anyone with an internet connect can mine CLOUD through a PoS system.</p>', NULL, NULL, 100000000.00, NULL, NULL, 0),
(26132, 'KMD', 'Komodo', '26132-KMD.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'dPoW/PoW', 'https://komodoplatform.com/', 'komodoplatform', '<p><span>Komodo is a privacy-centric cryptocurrency that combines the anonymity of ZCash with the security of Bitcoin. Using a new consensus mechanism developed by the Komodo team, delayed Proof of Work, Komodo blocks can be notarized using the Bitcoin blockchain. KMD is issued through an Equihash-based PoW</span><span> protocol, and the new block information is sent to pre-voted notary nodes. These nodes insert the Komodo block information on the BTC blockchain by creating a custom transaction. This system ensures that in order to "hack" komodo, one would have to rewrite both chains.</span><br /><br /><span>Komodo uses Zero Knowledge Proofs to provide 100% anonymous transactions, that are now secured with Bitcoin&#39;s hash rate</span>.</p>', NULL, NULL, 200000000.00, NULL, 'HitBTC~KMD~BTC,Binance~KMD~ETH,TradeSatoshi~KMD~LTC,Cryptopia~KMD~UNO,HitBTC~KMD~USD,HitBTC~KMD~ETH,TradeSatoshi~KMD~DOGE,CryptoX~KMD~BTC,Cryptopia~KMD~BTC,Cryptopia~KMD~LTC,BitTrex~KMD~BTC,Cryptopia~KMD~XMR,Cryptopia~KMD~DOT,TradeSatoshi~KMD~BTC,Binance~KMD~BTC,TradeSatoshi~KMD~BCH,Cryptopia~KMD~DOGE', 0),
(26194, 'GB', 'GoldBlocks', '26194-GB.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW/PoS', 'http://goldblocks.eu/', NULL, '<p>GoldBlocks is a gold based PoW/PoS cryptocurrency that is based on the idea of portable wealth.</p>', NULL, NULL, 50000000.00, NULL, 'CCEX~GB~LTC,Yobit~GB~WAVES,Bleutrade~GB~BTC,Yobit~GB~DOGE,LiveCoin~GB~BTC,CCEX~GB~BTC,Yobit~GB~RUR,Cryptsy~GB~XRP,Yobit~GB~ETH,TradeSatoshi~GB~BTC,Bleutrade~GB~DOGE,TradeSatoshi~GB~LTC,Yobit~GB~BTC,CCEX~GB~USD,Cryptsy~GB~BTC,CCEX~GB~DOGE,TradeSatoshi~GB~DOGE,Bleutrade~GB~ETH,Yobit~GB~USD,TradeSatoshi~GB~BCH', 0),
(27368, 'NEO', 'NEO', '27368-NEO.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://neo.org/', 'neo_blockchain', '<p>NEO is a platform in which users can issue and trade assets. NEO has been rebranded from the original &#39;Antshares&#39;. NEO <span>tokenizes proofs of ownership of an asset and not the asset itself, thus taking into account all of the legal complications and obligations that may come with the transfer of shares, equity and assets.</span></p><p>NEO represent an ownership of the NEO platform and allows users to buy NEO (ANC) and to vote on protocol changes on the NEO blockchain. ANS are 100% premined and issued on the NEO&#39;s genesis block.</p>', NULL, NULL, 100000000.00, NULL, 'Kucoin~NEO~USDT,LiveCoin~NEO~ETH,Quoine~NEO~SGD,OKEX~NEO~USDT,Bitfinex~NEO~USD,HuobiPro~NEO~USDT,Kucoin~NEO~KCS,Cryptopia~NEO~LTC,HitBTC~NEO~BTC,HuobiPro~NEO~BTC,Yunbi~NEO~CNY,Binance~NEO~BNB,Cryptopia~NEO~DOGE,Kucoin~NEO~BTC,Jubi~NEO~CNY,Gateio~NEO~USDT,Binance~NEO~USDT,Bitfinex~NEO~BTC,Quoine~NEO~JPY,Cryptopia~NEO~BTC,Bitfinex~NEO~ETH,LiveCoin~NEO~BTC,BitTrex~NEO~BTC,HitBTC~NEO~ETH,LiveCoin~NEO~USD,OKEX~NEO~BTC,Gateio~NEO~BTC,Quoine~NEO~USD,Binance~NEO~ETH,OKEX~NEO~ETH,Binance~NEO~BTC,BitTrex~NEO~USD,HitBTC~NEO~USD,BitTrex~NEO~ETH,Quoine~NEO~EUR,Kucoin~NEO~ETH', 0),
