(27594, 'MC', 'Mass Coin', '27594-MC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://mass.network/', 'network_mass', '<p>The Mass Network is a blockchain based system in which users are rewarded for their attention and data. The Mass Network software shields users&#39; data and allows them to set a price they are willing to accept for revealing it, thus creating a free market for advertisers and consumers, in which the websites act as mediators. Mass Coin (MC) is the native currency in the Mass Network system.</p>', NULL, NULL, 2147483648.00, NULL, NULL, 0),
