(321177, 'ELIX', 'Elixir', '321177-ELIX.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'http://elixirtoken.io/', 'elixtoken', '<p><span>Elixir is an Ethereum-based token created for lending services. It analyzes financial transactions and rewards borrowers for paying a loan installment on time. As so, Elixir is mined through transfers between pairs of addresses. In the lending service, these pairs of addresses will correspond to parties completing financial agreements<span>.</span></span></p>', NULL, NULL, 24147008.00, NULL, 'Kucoin~ELIX~ETH,Kucoin~ELIX~BTC,EtherDelta~ELIX~ETH', 0),
