(321347, 'HAC', 'Hackspace Capital', '321347-HAC.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://hackspace.capital/', 'hackspacecap', '<p>Hackspace Capital is a platform established in 2017 for the purpose of investing in technology hardware and connected hardware startups. These investments will be identified by its strategic partner, EnCata (engineering/prototyping company for hi-tech). The partnership is expected to bring to the public both a new cryptocurrency and blockchain eco-system as well as an ongoing series of hardware products and related services on which to spend the currency.</p><p>Token holders will be able to:</p><p>Exchange HAC tokens for goods and services produced by the HACKSPACE network of companies, and also for engineering services with minimal contracts and paperwork.</p><p>Users can also freely exchange HAC tokens for other crypto or fiat currencies on liquid exchanges or sell HAC tokens via the HackSpace platform to buyers interested in acquiring HackSpace goods and services.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1000000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~HAC~DOGE,HitBTC~HAC~BTC,Cryptopia~HAC~LTC,Cryptopia~HAC~BTC,Yobit~HAC~BTC,Yobit~HAC~WAVES,Yobit~HAC~ETH,Yobit~HAC~RUR,Yobit~HAC~DOGE,Yobit~HAC~USD', 0),
(321992, 'ADA', 'Cardano', '321992-ADA.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoS', 'https://www.cardanohub.org', 'cardanocom', '<p>Designed and developed by <span>IOHK in conjunction with the University of Edinburgh, the University of Athens and the University of Connecticut, C</span>ardano SL <span>(or Cardano Settlement Layer) is a Proof of Stake cryptocurrency based on the Haskell implementation of the white paper “Ouroboros: A Provably Secure Proof of Stake Blockchain Protocol” by Aggelos Kiayias, Alexander Russell, Bernardo David and Roman Oliynykov.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 2147483648.00, NULL, 'Gateio~ADA~BTC,Binance~ADA~ETH,Binance~ADA~BTC,BitTrex~ADA~USD,BitTrex~ADA~BTC,BitTrex~ADA~ETH,Gateio~ADA~USDT', 0),
