(346812, 'APPC', 'AppCoins', '346812-APPC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://appcoins.io', 'AppCoinsProject', '<div>AppCoins is a cryptocurrency for app stores that gives users new app purchasing power, unleashes monetization potential for developers and increases app safety.</div><div><div><span>This project provides developers a transparent and efficient way to monetise their apps and build a reputation across app stores; provides users a trusted environment with new purchasing possibilities and incentives to discover apps; and creates an app economy with a new universal language that ensures trust, transparency, and openness.</span></div></div>', NULL, NULL, 450000000.00, NULL, 'Binance~APPC~BTC,HuobiPro~APPC~BTC,EtherDelta~APPC~ETH,HuobiPro~APPC~ETH,Binance~APPC~BNB,Binance~APPC~ETH', 0),
(347067, 'WHL', 'WhaleCoin', '347067-WHL.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'https://whalecoin.org/', 'WhaleCoinOrg', '<p>Whalecoin is a decentralized social network that supports several types of roles and notably the “Whale” role which is given to any user who holds at least 1,000 tokens. Whales have the power to send upvotes to other users. The Whalecoin is a Proof of Work cryptocurrency based on the Ethash algorithm.  The Whalecoin blockchain will pay users a portion of the mined block reward based on how many upvotes a user receives from the Whales.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0),
(347235, 'BTG', 'Bitcoin Gold', '347235-BTG.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'PoW', 'https://bitcoingold.org/', 'bitcoingold', '<p>Bitcoin Gold is a fork of the Bitcoin blockchain that occurred at block 491407. It implements a new PoW algorithm, Equihash, which makes it ASIC-resistant and can only be mined by GPUs rigs. The purpose of Bitcoin Gold is to make mining decentralized again following Satoshi Nakamoto&#39;s vision of "1 CPU = 1 vote".</p>', NULL, NULL, 21000000.00, NULL, 'Cexio~BTG~BTC,BitFlip~BTG~EUR,BitBay~BTG~PLN,BitFlip~BTG~RUB,Yobit~BTG~RUR,Cexio~BTG~USD,QuadrigaCX~BTG~CAD,OKEX~BTG~BTC,OKEX~BTG~USDT,Coinone~BTG~KRW,Yobit~BTG~BTC,BitBay~BTG~USD,BitFlip~BTG~USD,HitBTC~BTG~BTC,QuadrigaCX~BTG~BTC,BitFlip~BTG~BTC,BitGrail~BTG~XRB,Novaexchange~BTG~BTC,Bithumb~BTG~KRW,HitBTC~BTG~USD,Binance~BTG~BTC,TradeSatoshi~BTG~BCH,BitBay~BTG~BTC,Yobit~BTG~ETH,Bleutrade~BTG~ETH,Yobit~BTG~DOGE,BitFlip~BTG~UAH,BitGrail~BTG~BTC,Kucoin~BTG~ETH,Cexio~BTG~EUR,BitZ~BTG~BTC,Yobit~BTG~WAVES,BitTrex~BTG~USD,TradeSatoshi~BTG~DOGE,Kucoin~BTG~BTC,Bitfinex~BTG~BTC,Binance~BTG~ETH,Abucoins~BTG~BTC,HuobiPro~BTG~BTC,TradeSatoshi~BTG~LTC,Gateio~BTG~BTC,BitBay~BTG~EUR,Gateio~BTG~USDT,Yobit~BTG~USD,Bleutrade~BTG~DOGE,BitTrex~BTG~ETH,TradeSatoshi~BTG~BTC,OKEX~BTG~BCH,Bleutrade~BTG~BTC,Bitfinex~BTG~USD,BitTrex~BTG~BTC,HitBTC~BTG~ETH', 0),
(347247, 'UP', 'UpToken', '347247-UP.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://uptoken.org/', 'UpToken', '<p>Coinme is a company that provides digital financial services. It will use the Ethereum blockchain to empower their cryptocurrency ATMs making them accessible in the throughout the world. Coinme also has features like a digital wallet and an exchange.</p><p>The<span> UpToken </span>will benefit the token holders with a 30% discount on ATM transaction fees, a reward program that will return 1% of an individual&#39;s total ATM transaction (cashback), and voting rights within the platform. </p>', NULL, NULL, 2147483648.00, NULL, 'EtherDelta~UP~ETH', 0),
