(370973, 'INS', 'INS Ecosystem', '370973-INS.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://www.ins.world', 'INS_Ecosystem', '<p>INS is the first global decentralized ecosystem that will enable consumers to buy groceries directly from manufacturers conveniently and at lower prices. The company will facilitate the direct interaction between consumers and manufacturers. Bypassing retailers and wholesalers means a more personalized and transparent grocery shopping experience at lower prices.</p><p>INS will enable manufacturers to create bespoke marketing programs to promote their goods directly to the consumers. These programs run on smart contracts and powered by the INS token as a means of reward.</p>', NULL, NULL, 100000000.00, NULL, 'Liqui~INS~USDT,Kucoin~INS~ETH,OKEX~INS~USDT,Binance~INS~BTC,OKEX~INS~BTC,Binance~INS~ETH,OKEX~INS~ETH,Liqui~INS~BTC,Liqui~INS~ETH,Kucoin~INS~BTC', 0),
(371004, 'TRCT', 'Tracto', '371004-TRCT.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'http://www.tracto.org/', 'Tracto14', '<p>Tracto (TRCT) is an open source peer-to-peer and business-to-customer cryptocurrency that offers secure, instant, decentralized and private transactions with unit value fungibility and Escrow function.</p>', NULL, NULL, 70000000.00, NULL, 'Tidex~TRCT~WAVES,Tidex~TRCT~ETH,Tidex~TRCT~BTC', 0),
(371005, 'UKG', 'UnikoinGold', '371005-UKG.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://unikoingold.com/', 'UnikoinGold', '<p>Unikrn is an e-sports entertainment and betting platform that will leverage the Ethereum blockchain to provide the users an easier and efficient way to obtain e-sports products and services. The Unikrn platform already has one token (Unikoin) used to buy products and participate on the platform (it will be replaced by the UnikoinSilver token). The team is now planning to create a utility token named as UnikoinGold (UKG), that will ease the use of the reward system implemented to benefit users who bet on e-sports. Furthermore, UKG token will also be used on a new skill-based betting platform.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1000000000.00, NULL, 'BitTrex~UKG~ETH,Kucoin~UKG~BTC,OKEX~UKG~BTC,BitTrex~UKG~BTC,OKEX~UKG~ETH,Kucoin~UKG~ETH,OKEX~UKG~USDT,EtherDelta~UKG~ETH', 0),
(371064, 'BTCRED', 'Bitcoin Red', '371064-BTCRED.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://www.bitcoinred.io/', 'BitcoinRed1', '<p>BTCRED is a community-driven and blockchain-enabled cryptocurrency working as an ERC20 token by leveraging the best attributes of both Bitcoin and Ethereum.</p>', NULL, NULL, 21000000.00, NULL, 'EtherDelta~BTCRED~ETH,Yobit~BTCRED~RUR,Yobit~BTCRED~USD,Yobit~BTCRED~ETH,Yobit~BTCRED~WAVES,Yobit~BTCRED~BTC,Yobit~BTCRED~DOGE', 0),
(371095, 'EBCH', 'eBitcoinCash', '371095-EBCH.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://ebitcoincash.io/', 'eBCHCoin', '<p><span>BitcoinCash has an issue with slow block times, ERC20 tokens don&#39;t have this issue and also have smart contract capability. There is currently no widely accepted tokenized version of BitcoinCash on Ethereum blockchain. The plan of the creators is to make this token widely accepted by pairing with fiat currencies (like USD, CNY, EURO, INR, etc.) and make this token as a token of choice for digital transactions.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 21000000.00, NULL, 'EtherDelta~EBCH~ETH', 0),
(371902, 'JPC*', 'J Coin', '371902-JPC.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'www.projectj.eu ', 'ProjectJ2017', '<p>Project J is building a cryptocurrency ecosystem with several key products or functions like the J-trex exchange, J-Visa card and J-wallet. J Coin is an ERC20 token on the Ethereum blockchain that will see 40% of the profits made through Project J distributed to token holders in the form of ETH.</p>', NULL, NULL, 100000000.00, NULL, 'Yobit~JPC*~USD,Yobit~JPC*~WAVES,BitTrex~JPC*~BTC,Yobit~JPC*~BTC,Yobit~JPC*~RUR,Yobit~JPC*~ETH,Yobit~JPC*~DOGE', 0),
