(372369, 'RDN*', 'Raiden Network', '372369-RDN.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://raiden.network/', 'raiden_network', '<p>The Raiden Network is an off-chain scaling payment solution to perform ERC20-compliant token transfers on the Ethereum blockchain. It is Ethereum&#39;s version of Bitcoin&#39;s Lightning Network, enabling near-instant, low-fee, scalable, and privacy-preserving payments.</p><p> </p>', NULL, NULL, 100000000.00, NULL, 'EtherDelta~RDN*~ETH,LAToken~RDN*~LA,OKEX~RDN*~USDT,Binance~RDN*~ETH,LAToken~RDN*~ETH,Gateio~RDN*~USDT,Kucoin~RDN*~BTC,Binance~RDN*~BTC,OKEX~RDN*~ETH,OKEX~RDN*~BTC,Binance~RDN*~BNB,Kucoin~RDN*~ETH,Gateio~RDN*~ETH', 0),
