(405291, 'TAU', 'Lamden Tau', '405291-TAU.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'DPoS', 'https://lamden.io/', 'LamdenTau', '<p>Lamden is a suite of developer tools that speed up the process of creating new and custom blockchains and apps. Lamden’s TAU token facilitates interoperability and value exchange between established cryptocurrencies and blockchain applications made with the Lamden developer suite.</p><p> </p>', NULL, NULL, 500000000.00, NULL, 'HitBTC~TAU~BTC', 0),
