(466977, 'DPP', 'Digital Assets Power Play', '466977-DPP.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://dapowerplay.com/', 'da_powerplay', '<p>The Digital Assets Power Play platform aims to enable the digital asset trading automation. The platform is organized around different stakeholders, wallets, and distributed compute nodes. Furthermore, the DA Power play team plans to provide a digital asset management, and an algorithm execution.</p><p>The Digital Assets Power Play token (DPP) is an ERC-20 token that will allow users to access the platform tools and services.</p><p> </p>', NULL, NULL, 100000000.00, NULL, 'Cryptopia~DPP~DOGE,Cryptopia~DPP~BTC,Cryptopia~DPP~LTC', 0),
(468052, 'ADB', 'Adbank', '468052-ADB.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 'https://adbank.network/', 'adbanknetwork', '<p><span>Adbank is an online ad platform built on the Ethereum blockchain. The platform will leverage the blockchain and AI technologies to remove the costly middlemen and also mitigate the $50 billion </span>problem<span><span> </span>of ad fraud. By using the Adbank platform, publishers will be able to get paid for their content while charging advertisers less and creating a transparent ecosystem that benefits all key stakeholders in the industry. Existing ad platforms will be able to access anti-fraud AI tools through<span> </span></span>Adbank’s<span><span> </span>API, which will be powered with ADB tokens.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 1000000000.00, NULL, 'Kucoin~ADB~BTC,Kucoin~ADB~ETH,EtherDelta~ADB~ETH', 0),
